This crate wraps the NanoVMs `ops` CLI (https://github.com/nanovms/ops),
which is distributed under the MIT License. The `ops` binary is invoked as
an external process; no upstream source is vendored into this crate.

Portions of this crate were originally authored inside the bare-cua
integration worktree (integration 014-nanovms-integration) and have been
promoted to the phenotype-shared (phenoShared) workspace for reuse by
bare-cua and helioscli integration 015.
